  "texts": [
    "By incorporating practical classes and activities, such as designing and producing their own works or building small robots, students are given opportunities to apply their knowledge and develop practical skills.",
    "This hands-on approach not only fosters creativity and critical thinking but also enhances students' problem-solving abilities.",
    "However, you mentioned that there are imbalances in educational resources, which can hinder the successful implementation of this reform.",
    "It is crucial to ensure that all schools have access to the necessary resources and support to provide high-quality education.",
    "This will help to bridge the gap and ensure that every student benefits from this educational reform."
  ]
